  "body": "This is a master issue to cover all issues related to routes and networks in the send flow.\r\n\r\n### Features\r\n\r\n- When a user selects a token and enters a value, the app should show the best route(s). \r\n- The user should be able to edit the receiver networks\r\n- The user should be able to disable some networks as the source\r\n- The user should be able to specify certain amount to be sent from a specific network\r\n\r\n[Designs.](https://www.figma.com/file/HKncH4wnDwZDAhc4AryK8Y/Wallet-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=7701-157501&mode=design&t=ixZfAk9WMF6w4KRx-4)\r\n\r\n### Issues\r\n\r\n- https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/issues/18248\r\n- https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/issues/18387\r\n- https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/issues/18278\r\n- https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/issues/18582\r\n- https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/issues/18655\r\n- https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/issues/18672",
